    <title>Norm</title>
    <link href="/2022/09/05/Norm/"/>
    <url>/2022/09/05/Norm/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="norm-長度的抽象概念"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#norm-長度的抽象概念"></a> Norm: 長度的抽象概念</h1><p>幫助測量矩陣、向量、函數等(非純量)的大小</p><h2 id="definition"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#definition"></a> Definition</h2><p>考慮<b>V</b>為一個向量空間(Vector space)，則說Norm為一個函數   <b>||·||：V → R</b>，且滿足：</p><ol><li>\( ||v|| ≥ 0, ||v||=0 ⇔ v=0 (長度非負) \)</li><li>For all \( α ∈ R, v ∈ V, ||αv||=|α| · ||v|| \)</li><li>For any \( v_1,v_2  ∈ V, ||v_1+v_2|| ≤ ||v_1|| + ||v_2|| (三角不等式) \)</li></ol><h2 id="三大常見的norm-norm定義的空間皆是向量空間"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#三大常見的norm-norm定義的空間皆是向量空間"></a> 三大常見的norm (norm定義的空間皆是向量空間)</h2><ol><li>\( R^n \)空間(有限維度空間)的norm</li></ol><center><img src="/img/Norm/R_VectorSpace_norm.png" width="70%" ["center"]></center><center>圖片來源：https://ch-hsieh.blogspot.com/2010/04/norm.html</center><br><ol start="2"><li>無窮維度空間的norm (<a href="#reference1">看Ref</a>)</li><li>定義在函數空間\(L^p-space \)的norm (<a href="#reference1">看Ref</a>)</li></ol><h2 id="induced-matrix-norm-矩陣的norm"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#induced-matrix-norm-矩陣的norm"></a> Induced Matrix Norm (矩陣的norm)</h2><h3 id="如何定義"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#如何定義"></a> 如何定義?</h3><p>先把矩陣變成向量，再算norm(上面定義了矩陣的norm)，叫做induced matrix norm，用一組向量把矩陣norm引(induce)出來。</p><h3 id="definition-2"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#definition-2"></a> Definition</h3><p>\( A ∈ R^{m \times n} \) (m x n Real matrix)：表linear map \( R^n → R^m \)</p><center> <b> p-norm of A: </b></center>$$ ||A||_p = max \frac{||Ax||_p}{||x||_p} $$$$ (x \in R^n, ||x||_p = 1) $$<ul><li>p = 1</li></ul><p><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi>A</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>a</mi><msub><mi>x</mi><mi>j</mi></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><munderover><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mi>m</mi></munderover><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><msub><mi>a</mi><mrow><mi>i</mi><mi>j</mi></mrow></msub><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">||A||_1 = max_j (\sum_{i=1}^{m}|a_{ij}|) </annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.30110799999999993em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight">1</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:2.929066em;vertical-align:-1.277669em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">m</span><span class="mord mathdefault">a</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault">x</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.311664em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight" style="margin-right:0.05724em;">j</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.286108em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mop op-limits"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.6513970000000002em;"><span style="top:-1.872331em;margin-left:0em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3.05em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span><span class="mrel mtight">=</span><span class="mord mtight">1</span></span></span></span><span style="top:-3.050005em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3.05em;"></span><span><span class="mop op-symbol large-op">∑</span></span></span><span style="top:-4.3000050000000005em;margin-left:0em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3.05em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">m</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.277669em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;"></span><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault">a</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.311664em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span><span class="mord mathdefault mtight" style="margin-right:0.05724em;">j</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.286108em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span></span></p><ul><li>p = 2<br>max eigenvalue $ \lambda_{max} $ of $ A^TA $，再開根號</li></ul><center> <b>maximum singular value of A </b></center>$$ ||A||_2 = \sqrt{\lambda_{max}(A^TA)} $$<div class="note primary"><p><b>English version</b></p><p>Help us to measure the magnitude of the non-scalar value, ex: matrix, vector, function,etc.</p></div><p><span id="reference1">Ref: <a href="https://ch-hsieh.blogspot.com/2010/04/norm.html">[數學分析] 淺談各種基本範數 (Norm)</a></span></p>]]></content>
    
    
